Package org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.ingredient.storage

Class IngredientComponentStorageSlottedInsertProxy<T,M>

java.lang.Object
org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.ingredient.storage.IngredientComponentStorageSlottedInsertProxy<T,M>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, org.cyclops.commoncapabilities.api.ingredient.storage.IIngredientComponentStorage<T,M>, org.cyclops.commoncapabilities.api.ingredient.storage.IIngredientComponentStorageSlotted<T,M>
public class IngredientComponentStorageSlottedInsertProxy<T,M> extends Object implements org.cyclops.commoncapabilities.api.ingredient.storage.IIngredientComponentStorageSlotted<T,M>
An ingredient component storage that only accepts insertions, and immediately forwards all insertions to another storage. Externally, this storage is exposed as inventory with a single empty slot.
